venue.name: NH Americans for Prosperity Field Office

item.description:
Join Americans for Prosperity as we kick off our field program here in New Hampshire by opening our new office in Manchester. Speakers will include AFP-NH Director Corey Lewandowski and State Senator Jim Forsythe, the lone senator to receive an A+ on our recent scorecard. Come learn abour AFP, how we plan to educate New Hampshire citizens about economic freedom, and how you can win great prizes by helping us out!

Free food and drink will be provided, and door prizes will be given out to a few lucky attendees.

Please RSVP at http://nhafp.eventbrite.com/.
item.name: Americans for Prosperity Office Opening Party ft Sen. Jim Forsythe
